# Google OAuth client ID for Drive sync (optional — app works without it).
# Create one at console.cloud.google.com:
#   1. New project → enable Google Drive API
#   2. OAuth consent screen → External → add drive.file scope → add yourself as test user
#   3. Credentials → OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web) → add authorized JS origins:
#      https://<your-netlify-site>.netlify.app and http://localhost:5173
# Copy the Client ID here and also add it to Netlify environment variables.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
